            <title>0.2.2</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 16:14:27 +0200</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.2.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.2.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<style>:root{color-scheme:light dark}body{font:14px/1.65 -apple-system,system-ui,sans-serif;color:#1d2122;margin:0;padding:16px 18px}h2{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 12px}ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px}li{margin:6px 0}li::marker{color:#f9a600}@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){body{color:#e7e9ea}}</style>
<h2>What’s new in 0.2.2</h2><ul>
<li>New projects now start from a clean slate — building a new site no longer rebuilds on top of a project you just closed</li>
<li>Components you build or promote are recognized on the canvas with a clear highlight, and editing one asks whether to change just that page or everywhere it is used</li>
<li>Built components get clean names (e.g. Faq) instead of the whole prompt</li>
<li>Polish: removed a stray gradient band on task cards in light and dark mode</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
